      <div class="card">
        <h1>Getting started</h1>
        <p>Install the SDK from the workspace and create a client with an auth cookie.</p>
        <pre><code>bun add tipply-sdk-ts</code></pre>
        <pre><code>import &#123; TipplyClient &#125; from "tipply-sdk-ts";

const client = new TipplyClient(&#123;
  authCookie: process.env.TIPPLY_AUTH_COOKIE,
&#125;);</code></pre>
        <p><a href="/sdk-reference">Read the SDK reference</a></p>
      </div>
